ğŸ“Œ C++ dagi barcha fayllar bilan ishlash headerlari
C++ tilida fayllar bilan ishlash uchun 3 ta asosiy header mavjud:

Header	Vazifasi	Misollar
<fstream>	Fayllarni oâ€˜qish va yozish (ifstream, ofstream, fstream)	std::ifstream, std::ofstream, std::fstream
<cstdio>	C uslubidagi fayl operatsiyalari (FILE*, fopen, fclose)	fopen(), fclose(), fgets()
<filesystem>	Fayl tizimini boshqarish (std::filesystem::path, exists())	std::filesystem::exists(), create_directory()
Keling, har birini batafsil tushuntiramiz va misollar bilan koâ€˜rib chiqamiz.

âŠ <fstream> - C++ fayl oqimlari (File Streams)
Vazifasi: C++ da fayllarni oâ€˜qish, yozish va tahrirlash uchun ishlatiladi.

Klass	Vazifasi	Misollar
std::ifstream	Fayldan oâ€˜qish (input file stream)	ifstream in("data.txt")
std::ofstream	Faylga yozish (output file stream)	ofstream out("data.txt")
std::fstream	Oâ€˜qish va yozish (file stream)	`fstream file("data.txt", ios::in
Misol: Faylga yozish va oâ€˜qish
cpp
ĞšĞ¾Ğ¿Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
Ğ ĞµĞ´Ğ°ĞºÑ‚Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
#include <iostream>
#include <fstream>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    // Faylga yozish
    ofstream yoz("example.txt");
    yoz << "Salom, dunyo!" << endl;
    yoz.close(); // Faylni yopish

    // Fayldan oâ€˜qish
    ifstream oqi("example.txt");
    string s;
    while (getline(oqi, s)) {
        cout << "Fayldan olingan: " << s << endl;
    }
    oqi.close();

    return 0;
}
ğŸ“Œ Qayerda qoâ€˜llaniladi?
âœ” Matn fayllarini yaratish, saqlash va oâ€˜qish
âœ” Log fayllarini yozish va kuzatish
âœ” Dastur sozlamalarini faylda saqlash

â‹ <cstdio> - C uslubidagi fayllar bilan ishlash
Vazifasi: C uslubidagi fayl operatsiyalari (FILE*, fopen, fclose) orqali ishlaydi.

Funksiya	Vazifasi	Misollar
fopen(filename, mode)	Fayl ochish	FILE* f = fopen("test.txt", "r")
fclose(f)	Faylni yopish	fclose(f)
fgets(buffer, size, f)	Fayldan qator oâ€˜qish	fgets(buf, 100, f)
fprintf(f, format, ...)	Faylga yozish	fprintf(f, "Hello %d", 10)
fscanf(f, format, ...)	Fayldan oâ€˜qish	fscanf(f, "%d", &x)
fseek(f, offset, whence)	Fayl kursorini siljitish	fseek(f, 0, SEEK_END)
Misol: Faylga yozish va oâ€˜qish (C uslubi)
cpp
ĞšĞ¾Ğ¿Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
Ğ ĞµĞ´Ğ°ĞºÑ‚Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
#include <cstdio>

int main() {
    FILE* fayl = fopen("test.txt", "w");
    fprintf(fayl, "Salom, fayl!\n");
    fclose(fayl);

    char buffer[100];
    fayl = fopen("test.txt", "r");
    fgets(buffer, 100, fayl);
    fclose(fayl);

    printf("Fayldan oâ€˜qildi: %s", buffer);
    return 0;
}
ğŸ“Œ Qayerda qoâ€˜llaniladi?
âœ” Eski C dasturlarida
âœ” Kam resurs talab qiluvchi tizimlarda (microcontroller, OS)
âœ” Binar fayllar bilan ishlashda

âŒ <filesystem> - Fayl tizimini boshqarish (C++17)
Vazifasi: Fayllar va papkalar bilan ishlash (yaratish, oâ€˜chirish, mavjudligini tekshirish).

Funksiya	Vazifasi	Misollar
std::filesystem::exists(path)	Fayl yoki katalog borligini tekshirish	exists("data.txt")
std::filesystem::remove(path)	Fayl yoki katalogni oâ€˜chirish	remove("old.txt")
std::filesystem::create_directory(path)	Katalog yaratish	create_directory("new_folder")
std::filesystem::file_size(path)	Fayl hajmini olish	file_size("data.txt")
std::filesystem::rename(old, new)	Fayl nomini oâ€˜zgartirish	rename("old.txt", "new.txt")
Misol: Fayl borligini tekshirish va katalog yaratish
cpp
ĞšĞ¾Ğ¿Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
Ğ ĞµĞ´Ğ°ĞºÑ‚Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ñ‚ÑŒ
#include <iostream>
#include <filesystem>
using namespace std;
namespace fs = std::filesystem;

int main() {
    string filename = "data.txt";

    if (fs::exists(filename)) {
        cout << filename << " mavjud!" << endl;
    } else {
        cout << filename << " mavjud emas!" << endl;
    }

    fs::create_directory("test_folder"); // Yangi katalog yaratish
    return 0;
}
ğŸ“Œ Qayerda qoâ€˜llaniladi?
âœ” Fayllarning mavjudligini tekshirish
âœ” Kataloglarni avtomatik yaratish
âœ” Fayl va katalog boshqarish tizimlari

ğŸ¯ Xulosa
C++ da fayllar bilan ishlash uchun 3 ta asosiy header mavjud:

1ï¸âƒ£ <fstream> â†’ Eng koâ€˜p ishlatiladigan C++ fayl oqimlari
2ï¸âƒ£ <cstdio> â†’ C uslubidagi fayl operatsiyalari (FILE*)
3ï¸âƒ£ <filesystem> â†’ Fayl tizimini boshqarish (exists(), create_directory())

Qachon ishlatish kerak?
âœ… Faylni ochish va matn yozish â†’ <fstream>
âœ… C uslubidagi operatsiyalar (FILE*) â†’ <cstdio>
âœ… Fayl yoki katalog borligini tekshirish â†’ <filesystem>
